usage: spec-anchor core [-h] [--all] [--rebuild] [--verify-index]
                        [--llm-provider LLM_PROVIDER_ID]
                        [--decision-json DECISION_JSON]
                        [--decision-file DECISION_FILE]

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --all, -a             clear LLM-derived caches (section metadata + pair
                        typing + chapter anchors) and re-evaluate
  --rebuild             drop and recreate the Qdrant spec_anchor_section
                        collection (implies --all). Use when embeddings are
                        suspected corrupt or the collection has stale residue.
  --verify-index        verify that the Qdrant Source Retrieval Index payloads
                        match the current section hashes
  --llm-provider LLM_PROVIDER_ID
                        configured [llm.providers.<id>] to use for this /spec-
                        core run
  --decision-json DECISION_JSON
                        JSON conflict decision payload to pass to /spec-core
  --decision-file DECISION_FILE
                        path to a JSON conflict decision payload to pass to
                        /spec-core
